_:N10827c91ee574d3b963bc701d1ea1275 <http://schema.org/description> "We serve and support ex-servicemen and women, their widows or widowers and their immediate family members. We are an independent voice, here to help you whenever or wherever you served, whether in World War 2 or Afghanistan. VAPC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Defence ." .
